<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>To-Label - room</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue/dist/vue.js"></script>
    <script
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.0.js"
      integrity="sha256-JlqSTELeR4TLqP0OG9dxM7yDPqX1ox/HfgiSLBj8+kM="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: rgb(249, 245, 253)">
    <header class="pt-3" style="padding-left: 1.1rem">
      <nav
        class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark"
        style="position: fixed; left: 0; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100"
      >
        <div class="container">
          <a
            class="navbar-brand"
            href="/home"
            style="
              font-size: 5vh;
              font-weight: bold;
              position: relative;
              left: -5%;
            "
            >To-Label</a
          >
          <button
            class="navbar-toggler"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
            aria-controls="navbarNav"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-label="Toggle navigation"
            style="height: 6vh; width: 7vh; position: relative; right: -5%"
          >
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon" style="font-size: 3vh"></span>
          </button>
          <div
            class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end"
            style="margin: 4vh"
            id="navbarNav"
          >
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="#" style="height: 4vh">
                  <i
                    class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"
                    style="font-size: 4vh"
                  ></i>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item dropdown" style="height: 5vh">
                <a
                  class="nav-link dropdown-toggle"
                  href="#"
                  id="navbarDropdown"
                  role="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  style="font-size: 5vh; position: relative; top: -1.5vh"
                >
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-user" style="height: 5vh"></i>
                  <!-- ユーザーアイコンの画像ファイルへのパス -->
                </a>
                <ul
                  class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end bg-dark"
                  aria-labelledby="navbarDropdown"
                >
                  <li>
                    <a
                      class="dropdown-item text-white"
                      href="/history"
                      style="font-size: 4vh; font-weight: bold"
                      >History</a
                    >
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <a
                      class="dropdown-item text-white"
                      href="/setting"
                      style="font-size: 4vh; font-weight: bold"
                      >Setting</a
                    >
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <a
                      class="dropdown-item text-white"
                      href="/help"
                      style="font-size: 4vh; font-weight: bold"
                      >Help</a
                    >
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <a
                      class="dropdown-item text-white"
                      href="/logout"
                      style="font-size: 4vh; font-weight: bold"
                      >Logout</a
                    >
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main
      style="position: absolute; top: 18vh; left: 5%; width: 90%; z-index: -100"
    >
      <h1 class="text-center">レッテルの結果!!!</h1>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header"><%= username %></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <% your_msg_list.forEach(element =>{%>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header"><%= element.from_username %></div>
            <div class="card-body"><%= element.msg %></div>
          </div>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% other_msg_list.forEach(element=>{%>
      <div class="card mt-4">
        <div class="card-header"><%= element[0] %></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <% element[1].forEach(child=>{%>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header"><%= child.from_username %></div>
            <div class="card-body"><%= child.msg %></div>
          </div>
          <%})%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>
        この部屋は、1日経つと削除されて、アクセスできなくなります。明日以降は、ユーザーのプロフィールページより閲覧ください。
      </p>
      <%})%>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
